		<a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=16&mode=details&type=races'>Shadow Knight</a>, <a href='http://www.everlore.com/races_classes/classes.asp?CID=12&mode=details&type=races'>Necromancer</a>
     </font>
    
    </td>
  </tr>
