			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Giest was right. Here's a copy of the official word.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
I don't know if this has been answered a lot or I'm just out of it, but: do pets take a share of experience? <BR>
<BR>
Pets always get a share of the experience. If the pet owner is in a group, they take up to 1% of the group experience. If the pet owner is solo, they take much much more. In other words, don't tell that magician &quot;Axe the pet&quot; if all you are worried about is experience. <BR>
<BR>
-Gordon<BR>

