				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				There is also another command for your pet.<BR>
<BR>
/pet guard here<BR>
<BR>
This will make your pet stand in one place and attack anything hostile to you.  If you get hit he will run over to the fight and then return to his spot when done fighting.<BR>
<BR>
Very useful when scouting so that things wont attack your lower level pet.
